ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------
For now this only contains client libs and binaries

Irix 5.3 specific notes:
OpenLDAP needs a POSIX compatible regex implementation but Irix 5.3 doesn't
provide it. To fix this I added support for pcre since it contains a
POSIX regex compatibility layer (pcreposix).
